@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### List all loans (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/loans

### Create a loan (replace with real IDs)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "<REPLACE_USER_ID>",
  "bookId": "<REPLACE_BOOK_ID>"
}

### Return a loan (replace :id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/loans/{{loanId}}/return

### Loans by user (replace :userId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/loans/user/{{userId}}

